 sepulchral epigrams as a poetic art on the other.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aEpigrams, GreekxHistory and criticism. 0aEpitaphszGreecexHistory and criticism. 0aFuneral rites and ceremonies in literature. 0aFuneral rites and ceremonieszGreece. 4aEpigramm. 4aGrabinschrift. 4aInschrift. 7aHISTORY / Ancient / Greece.2bisacsh  aFunerary Inscription.  aGreek Epigram.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Classics and Near East Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110636178oZDB-23-GCN08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2008z9783110212129oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2008z978311021213608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET ALTERTUM 2008z9783110209075oZDB-23-DGD0 cprintz978311020132140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311021165840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110211658423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110211658/original  a978-3-11-021213-6  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2008b2008  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGDb2008  aZDB-23-DGGb2008  aZDB-23-GCNc2000d2014